table concurrent_futures_extra204.cf_code_flag_values:
  description: "concurrent.futures function __code__.co_flags and co_stacksize value checks in cfcoflags204 namespace — wait.co_flags==67108867 (CO_OPTIMIZED|CO_NEWLOCALS; same value as abc.abstractmethod and abc.update_abstractmethods); as_completed.co_flags==67108899 (includes CO_GENERATOR=32 because as_completed uses yield to produce futures as they complete); ThreadPoolExecutor.__init__.co_flags==201326603 (regular method with high interpreter optimization flags); wait.co_stacksize==8; as_completed.co_stacksize==10 (larger because generator logic is more complex); ThreadPoolExecutor.__init__.co_stacksize==5; verified with Python 3.14.3"
